    (?\< . "\\textless{}")
    (?\> . "\\textgreater{}")
    (?^  . "\\^{}")
    (?\~ . "\\~{}")
    (?\@ . "\\@")
    (?\$ . "\\$")
    (?\% . "\\%")
    (?\{ . "\\{")
    (?\} . "\\}")
    (?\& . "\\&")
    (?\# . "\\#"))
  "A table of characters which must be represented specially.
These are applied to the entire document, sans already-escaped
